ygData.messageBody:
If you get this then you're on the list!

First piece of advice: check out the very cool class-specific
information online at : http://everquest.gamestats.com - don't worry
about the equipment info, nor the quest stuff, just follow the links
under Paladin. Next, check out the Paladin Class info at
http://eq.stratics.com

Once you have taken all that information in, you should have some
specific questions such as best places to hunt, whom to group with, what
equipment to be looking for, etc, which this list excels at helping you
with.

Learn first, then prosper, Paladin!

Kaladin, proud 17th level Holy Warrior of Tunare
